	</listitem>
	<listitem><para>The above method downloads formatted databases. You can also
	download unformatted databases from ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/db/FASTA/.
	If you've used the update_db.pl tool or downloaded the databases from 
	ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/db/, then DO NOT run formatdb.</para>
	<para>Run the formatdb
	command to format the database to the BLAST format. For this example,
	we'll use the Drosophila Melanogaster (fruitfly) nucleotide database</para>
	<screen>
-bash-3.1$ wget -q ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/db/FASTA/drosoph.nt.gz
-bash-3.1$ gunzip drosoph.nt.gz 
-bash-3.1$ formatdb -p F -V T -i drosoph.nt 
-bash-3.1$ ls drosoph.nt*
